CLASS zcl_20_hello_world DEFINITION  PUBLIC  FINAL  CREATE PUBLIC .    PUBLIC SECTION.      INTERFACES if_oo_adt_classrun .  PROTECTED SECTION.  PRIVATE SECTION.ENDCLASS.      CLASS zcl_20_hello_world IMPLEMENTATION.      METHOD if_oo_adt_classrun~main.      CONSTANTS name TYPE c LENGTH 10 VALUE 'David'.    DATA text TYPE string.      CONCATENATE 'Hello_'                name                INTO text.      TYPES my_type TYPE p LENGTH 3 DECIMALS 2.    DATA my_var TYPE my_type.    my_var = '150.5'.      DATA lv_carrier TYPE /dmo/carrier_id.    lv_carrier = 'XXX'.      DATA(output) = |{ text } your var is { my_var } and your carrier is { lv_carrier }|.      do 10 times.        out->write( output ).    enddo.      ENDMETHOD.ENDCLASS.

